        <p>&nbsp;</p>         <p> </p><p>Page layouts provide structure to your page — two-column, three-column, and more — making it <br />easy for everyone in your organization, first-time and power users alike, to create beautiful pages.</p><p> </p><ol><li><span style="color: rgb(51,51,51);"><strong>Edit</strong> the page.</span></li><li><span style="color: rgb(51,51,51);">Click the <strong>Page Layout</strong></span> button in the editor toolbar. It looks like this:<br /><span style="color: rgb(51,51,51);"><img class="confluence-embedded-image" src="/confluence/download/attachments/98308/step07-00.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1387518917000&amp;api=v2" data-image-src="/confluence/download/attachments/98308/step07-00.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1387518917000&amp;api=v2" data-linked-resource-id="163861" data-linked-resource-type="attachment" data-linked-resource-default-alias="step07-00.jpg" data-base-url="http://10.2.1.106:8080/confluence" data-linked-resource-container-id="98308" title="Demonstration Space > Lay out your page (step 6 of 9) > step07-00.jpg" data-location="Demonstration Space > Lay out your page (step 6 of 9) > step07-00.jpg"> <br /> </span></li><li><span style="color: rgb(51,51,51);">Select the <strong>Two-Column</strong></span> page layout.<br /><span style="color: rgb(51,51,51);"><img class="confluence-embedded-image" src="/confluence/download/attachments/98308/step07-01.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1387518917000&amp;api=v2" data-image-src="/confluence/download/attachments/98308/step07-01.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1387518917000&amp;api=v2" data-linked-resource-id="163858" data-linked-resource-type="attachment" data-linked-resource-default-alias="step07-01.jpg" data-base-url="http://10.2.1.106:8080/confluence" data-linked-resource-container-id="98308" title="Demonstration Space > Lay out your page (step 6 of 9) > step07-01.jpg" data-location="Demonstration Space > Lay out your page (step 6 of 9) > step07-01.jpg"><br /><br /></span></li><li><span style="color: rgb(51,51,51);">Select the <strong>Three-Column with Header and Footer</strong></span><span style="color: rgb(51,51,51);"> page layout.</span><br /><span style="color: rgb(51,51,51);"><img class="confluence-embedded-image" src="/confluence/download/attachments/98308/step07-02.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1387518917000&amp;api=v2" data-image-src="/confluence/download/attachments/98308/step07-02.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1387518917000&amp;api=v2" data-linked-resource-id="163862" data-linked-resource-type="attachment" data-linked-resource-default-alias="step07-02.jpg" data-base-url="http://10.2.1.106:8080/confluence" data-linked-resource-container-id="98308" title="Demonstration Space > Lay out your page (step 6 of 9) > step07-02.jpg" data-location="Demonstration Space > Lay out your page (step 6 of 9) > step07-02.jpg"><br /> </span></li><li><span style="color: rgb(51,51,51);">Use your cursor (or press </span>Ctrl+A or Cmd+A)<span style="color: rgb(51,51,51);"> to highlight all the content in this page layout block.</span></li><li><span style="color: rgb(51,51,51);">Copy and paste this content into the center and right-hand content blocks.</span></li><li>Click <strong>Save</strong>.</li></ol><h1 style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(51,51,51);"><br /></span></h1><h1 style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(51,51,51);"><a class="confluence-link" href="/confluence/pages/viewpage.action?pageId=98314" data-linked-resource-id="98314" data-linked-resource-type="page" data-linked-resource-default-alias="Get serious with a table (step 5 of 9)" data-base-url="http://10.2.1.106:8080/confluence"><img class="confluence-embedded-image" src="/confluence/download/attachments/98305/prev.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1387518917000&amp;api=v2" data-image-src="/confluence/download/attachments/98305/prev.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1387518917000&amp;api=v2" data-linked-resource-id="163868" data-l